sub_title: Founder at Bit Shufflers Holding BV
summary:
Hello, 

Below you may find a short summary of my current IT experience and goals. For CV and descriptions of my projects, please contact me directly.

Adam Grodowski,
agrodowski@pm.me

Functional skills:
▪ Development of IT systems and services (Java EE / Python / Groovy expertise)
▪ Solution/Data/Technical Architecture (ArchiMate 3.1 certified, TOGAF - in progress)
▪ Management and support (Tech, PM)
▪ Service delivery (European Patent Office)
▪ DevOps: Jenkins, K8s, Azure
▪ Knowledge of Computer Vision: text detection, CNN image classification
▪ Knowledge of Blockchain: Smart Contracts (Solidity)
▪ Knowledge of Machine Translation: SMT, NMT
▪ Knowledge of Cryptography: RSA, ECC, Lattice
▪ Data Mining: Predictive/Descriptive analysis, advanced statistical modelling, machine learning
▪ Text Mining: information retrieval, named entity recognition (legal persons, products, journal names), 
 basic relationship extraction
▪ Knowledge of Mobile Networks (~10 years old): HSPA/3G/3.5G/3G+ access & radio layers dimensioning
